1. Create Profile (one-time setup)
    a. Detect, Label & Save all attached displays (main board, HUD, DM screen, Ambiance)
        i. Main board - Would you like to use embedded or external Aruco markers?
        ii. Where would you like to display HUD (Main board, DM screen, dedicated HUD screen, nowhere)
    b. Detect, Select & Save preferred webcam
        i. Generate Charuco board, Camera Warp Calibration, save distortion values


1b. Web version
    a. can't detect attached displays, so just generate URLs as needed
    b. can't detect webcams, so save webcam profile
    c. upload map/select saved map

2. Table Setup (every session)
    a. Display setup
        i. Please select a map you'd like to use.
        ii. Detect resolution of image and display, display mockup, allow repositions/resizing
        iii. Generate grid with slider bars AND numerical input, then "lock"
    b. Table Tracking Setup
        i. Please place camera on tripod with all 4 Aruco markers in frame.
        ii. Detect Aruco markers, adjust size, border and alpha value independently for each marker
        iii. Generate homography output and generate grid labels
        iv. take background frame for difference_mask/motion_mask
    c. Miniature tracking setup
        i. label initial miniatures

3. Begin gameplay


